desc_long								关于这款游戏							Cruel Arena is a classic arena survival zombie game. Face endless hordes and survive as much as you can, Through The Doodles and The Frames!! Will you do the best record among your friends?A few tips:-Press S to buy something.-Always, Always, Always keep yourself in movement! Learn how to move and they will never catch you!-WASD to move, left mouse to shoot, and right one to throw a granade!-P to PAUSE.-That's all, get ready!						
